data.description: Rare opening in Evergreen Estates! The quiet, tucked-back neighborhood is known for its large lots and peaceful community. This 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home situated on .73 acres is ready for new memories and your own personal touches! You'll love the spacious kitchen that seamlessly flows into the light-filled dining nook and living room. Upstairs you'll find the generous primary suite with a sitting area overlooking the expansive backyard, large walk-in closet, and ensuite with soaking tub. Ideal floorpan! Step outside and enjoy the large, level lot with low-maintenance landscaping. Take advantage of the oversized 3 car garage and an exterior parking pad! Enjoy convenient access to Downtown Hillsboro, nearby parks and schools, HWY 26, and the Intel campus.
